  "title": "Gooey Indulgent Ethiopian Gorgonzola Dabo",
  "description": "Rich and molten Ethiopian dish featuring gorgonzola-dolce, cooked in a clay pot, this satvik-friendly recipe is a twist on traditional dabo.",
